### Automatic Installation
- All `npm install` commands should be executed automatically by Cursor
- No user approval required for npm installations
- Install missing dependencies automatically when detected

### Package Installation Guidelines
- Install packages when import statements reference missing modules
- Install dev dependencies when build tools are missing
- Install peer dependencies automatically
- Update package-lock.json automatically

### Package.json Management
- Keep package.json organized with proper categorization
- Use exact versions for critical dependencies
- Use caret (^) for minor version updates in development dependencies
- Document all dependencies with clear purposes


